doctype html
html(lang="es")
	head
		title Spettacolo TV
		link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Ubuntu:400,300,500,700|Droid+Serif:400,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css')
		link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.5.0/css/font-awesome.min.css")
		link(rel="stylesheet" href="css/app.css")
	body

		header(class="Header")
			div(class="medium")
				h1(class="Header-title") Spettacolo TV
				div(class="Header-form")
					form(action="" class="form")
						input(type="text" placeholder="Buscar un Show de TV")
						span(class="fa fa-search")

		section(class="Shows medium")
			article(class="Shows-show")
				figure(class="Shows-show-cover")
					img(class="img" src="img/the-100.jpg")
					figcaption(class="Shows-show-cover-name")
						span The 100
				div(class="Shows-show-data")
					p(class="Shows-show-data-nextepisode") Stealing Fire
					p(class="Shows-show-data-description") Season one of The 100 saw the human race return, after a 97-year exile in space, to a wildly transformed Earth...only to discover that the human race had never truly left. Clarke found herself forced to lead a band of disposable juvenile delinquents as they faced death at every turn - from a world transformed by radiation, from the fierce Grounders who somehow managed to survive in it, and, perhaps worst of all, from themselves.
		
		footer(class="Footer")
			p(class="Footer-total")
				span(class="Footer-total-num") 167
				span(class="Footer-total-exp") Episodios existentes

		script(src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.1.min.js")
		script(src="js/app.js")